<lb />3) satisfactory information, freedom from doubt, certainty: <cit><quote>I would unstate myself, to be in a due r.</quote> <bibl n="shak. lr 1.2.108" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. I, 2, 108</bibl></cit>.
